{"tid":1519702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"cls 好撚慘d狗","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:51:22.000Z","uid":23471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"618abf0b15b6d898e5e74284756f9d5a94ef537c","tid":1519702,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"反對警方冷血言論，罔顧動物健康及安全，同意請廣傳！<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台日前拍得警方帶同一隻沒配戴任何保護裝備的警犬，步出催淚煙滿佈的現場，警員當時卻全部戴上軍用防毒面罩。<br />\n<br />\n在警方記者會上，記者指警犬有機會吸到催淚煙，問警方安排是否恰當，警察公共關係科總警司謝振中隨即反駁說警犬吸到催淚煙，「我看不到身體有任何問題！」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n催淚彈屬於化武，含山埃毒氣，可對身體構成長期損害，小動物比人類更敏感脆弱，對牠們傷害更大。<br />\n<br />\n催淚毒氣並非水溶性，有毒物質會殘留在社區，有時更難以清除（例如黏附在軟家具），有需要時要扔掉。"},{"pid":"45e1b7c6cf0186237f2ed3b049e18821ff36a9eb","tid":1519702,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求入來推po！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士請快D碌入來！！！ 更新了整合名單，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1518567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9e9e8317b6644a5e5ea746befd503aed745c42f0","tid":1519702,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"班仆街失曬控 聽日大家小心"},{"pid":"cca6a6dd25c3cf8aa7788e6b3c3ddcb5aba4b885","tid":1519702,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a741943d84d574a73f3fb1a03461aa8319d8994","tid":1519702,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷